                            <comment id="13830823" author="jbellis" created="Sun, 24 Nov 2013 01:32:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in cassandra-2.0 HEAD.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that you probably shouldn&apos;t use multithreaded compaction.  (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6142&quot; title=&quot;Remove multithreaded compaction (and precompactedrow)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-6142&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-6142&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13830824" author="gwicke" created="Sun, 24 Nov 2013 01:44:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ahh, good to know. I suspected something along those lines, so started a run with multithreaded_compaction disabled. So far (four hours in) it is looking good.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
